race.description: Sires On Ice (Wa) Young Stars Classic H
race.comment: NEXT THING UNO (8) turned in a plain effort last time when fifth at Q Lakeside over 457m behind Kisses For Me (26.20) in a OPEN. Was a winner the start prior. Tough to beat if on-song. CHEF'S DREAM (1) goes very well this trip starting 25 times for nine wins and 14 minors. Scored by 4 lengths last time (30.05) in a Grade 5 over 520m at this track. Suited here and expected to run well. TIC TAC MONELLI (6) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and three minors from nine tries. Placed last time (27.54) at Mandurah in a Grade 5/6, finishing second and beaten 4 lengths. Can feature with the right run. OOSTHUIZEN (4) cannot be left out after placing here at this trip last start.
